Docker display:
DISPLAY=$DISPLAY
DISPLAY=:0

docker run -ti --rm \
    -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY \
    -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix \
    -v $HOME/.Xauthority:$HOME/.Xauthority \
    -net=host \
    firefox


http://fabiorehm.com/blog/2014/09/11/running-gui-apps-with-docker/
http://wiki.ros.org/docker/Tutorials/GUI
